thread.title: Janet

author: Janet
title: Janet
text:
I recently had the pleasure of working with a highly motivated team of property consultants, at Nelson Alexander in Preston to prepare my house for sale. At each stage of the campaign the team showed a high level of professionalism, personalised communication and eye to detail. The auction was a great success and I am delighted with the outcome.
Thanks to Michelle Portelli and her team !!
